SUMMARY:Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club discusses Can't We Talk About Something More Pleasant?
DESCRIPTION:This Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club meeting will take place via Zoom. The Zoom link will be the same for every meeting and will be provided in your Eventbrite email receipt (scroll down to the Additional Information section). \n  \n \nOn June 30\, 2026 the Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club will discuss Can’t We Talk About Something More Pleasant?: A Memoir by Roz Chast. \nInprint BCM HEAL Book Club meetings are free and designed for those involved in the healthcare community. Meetings are facilitated by Stacy Nigliazzo. The full schedule of Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club meetings for 2026 appears on the main Inprint BCM HEAL Book Club webpage\, which you can access by\, clicking here. \nIf you have any further questions\, please email info@inprint.org. \n
URL:https://inprinthouston.org/event/inprint-bcm-heal-book-club-discusses-cant-we-talk-about-something-more-pleasant/
LOCATION:Online via Zoom
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://inprinthouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Cant-We-Talk-About-Something-More-Pleasant.jpg
END:VEVENT
